text: Arsen Śliwiński (born 3 April 1996) is a Polish sprint canoeist. He participated at the 2017 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships and 2018 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.C-2 200 m resultsC-2 500 m results ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Polish male canoeists Category:Living people Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in Canadian
